1
00:01:44,700 --> 00:01:45,670
Why

2
00:01:53,210 --> 00:01:55,330
Why can’t you admit I’m still in your heart?

3
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:05,620
Why did you leave without telling anyone? Why?

4
00:02:11,030 --> 00:02:12,170
I’m sorry

5
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,460
That’s not what I want to hear

6
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:18,620
I want to know what happened in all those years

7
00:02:19,550 --> 00:02:29,320
Why did you come back? Why did you change your name? Why did you show up again in my life?

8
00:02:29,590 --> 00:02:31,900
Have you thought about my feelings? Have you?

9
00:02:39,900 --> 00:02:41,340
I want to know, Zeyi

10
00:02:42,690 --> 00:02:45,050
I want to what has happened to you

11
00:02:47,860 --> 00:02:52,110
I want to know what stands between us

12
00:02:55,870 --> 00:03:00,980
I want to know if our promises still count

13
00:03:15,940 --> 00:03:17,880
I want to start over with you

14
00:03:28,510 --> 00:03:36,200
But I want to know if you still love me

15
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,730
Come to a place with me

16
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:11,200
[18. I want to give you that late promise]

17
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,590
Mr.Xiang, you are here

18
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:27,320
How it it? -All fine. Don’t you want to come in?

19
00:04:57,700 --> 00:04:58,970
Who is he?

20
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:11,950
His name is Gu Yishan, he is Xu Wenjie’s ex-boyfriend

21
00:05:15,490 --> 00:05:17,540
Xu Wenjie’s ex-boyfriend

22
00:05:18,340 --> 00:05:23,630
Days before we graduated, an accident happened

23
00:05:32,170 --> 00:05:34,110
And he’s been in coma since then

24
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:43,550
Why have you never brought him up?

25
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:47,220
What does his coma have anything to do with you?

26
00:05:50,550 --> 00:05:51,940
It was my fault

27
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:59,070
If I could have been more calm

28
00:06:18,530 --> 00:06:24,460
He could be just like us now, standing here well

29
00:06:32,510 --> 00:06:33,840
No one would forgive me

30
00:06:34,810 --> 00:06:36,380
I don’t deserve to be forgiven

31
00:06:37,770 --> 00:06:42,350
After I was released, I began to try to find him

32
00:06:45,060 --> 00:06:49,030
Until I met Gu Wenjie. She’d been taking care of him

33
00:06:57,810 --> 00:07:00,380
I thought I’d washed out all of sins

34
00:07:04,220 --> 00:07:18,460
But the first time I met him, I began to realize that it all just began

35
00:07:27,610 --> 00:07:32,660
At that time, I dared not to sleep

36
00:07:35,140 --> 00:07:42,390
Every time I closed my eyes, that accident happened in front of me

37
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,050
I hurt him bad

38
00:07:52,780 --> 00:07:54,290
I ruined his life

39
00:07:58,990 --> 00:08:04,760
Don’t be like that. It was just an accident -Not just an accident

40
00:08:12,090 --> 00:08:13,980
I also ruined my parents’s life

41
00:08:27,390 --> 00:08:28,750
Before that

42
00:08:35,020 --> 00:08:37,480
I didn’t know how to face you

43
00:08:54,980 --> 00:09:00,680
Even if it was a nightmare, we can face it together

44
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:11,170
All these years, you’ve kept that secret for yourself

45
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:13,920
It’s hard enough for you to face it on your own

46
00:09:22,940 --> 00:09:24,420
From now on

47
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,050
We are facing it together

48
00:09:30,260 --> 00:09:32,280
We will make it through

49
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:05,520
Honey, you are up. Come here, I’m making you breakfast

50
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:13,690
What’s wrong?

51
00:10:13,950 --> 00:10:16,020
Honey

52
00:10:18,140 --> 00:10:21,680
Are you alright? -Sure

53
00:10:23,530 --> 00:10:28,110
Is it wrong for wife making breakfast for her husband?

54
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,400
Try this, husband

55
00:10:33,180 --> 00:10:36,520
What, do you hate it? -Of course not

56
00:10:41,490 --> 00:10:42,990
Tastes good?

57
00:10:45,620 --> 00:10:48,000
Michelin three stars

58
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:51,550
Have some more

59
00:10:52,110 --> 00:10:57,180
Am I behaving well today? -Of course

60
00:10:57,840 --> 00:11:03,630
Do I deserve some rewards?

61
00:11:07,780 --> 00:11:11,560
Of course you do. Name it and I’ll buy it

62
00:11:11,860 --> 00:11:16,450
Not that. Honey -Yes -I don’t need vulgar things

63
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:24,640
I just want a little tip about that surprise

64
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:28,360
Are you still thinking about that?

65
00:11:28,640 --> 00:11:37,470
I’m just curious, honey, I promise I’ll act like I don’t know

66
00:11:37,710 --> 00:11:43,390
You always act like this and then you blame me for not being romantic

67
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:51,890
I’m not saying anything this time, just come back home Friday and I’ll surprise you

68
00:11:52,940 --> 00:11:55,840
You are making me more curious

69
00:11:56,130 --> 00:12:00,060
Just tell me, honey -No

70
00:12:00,290 --> 00:12:03,350
I’ll kill myself if you don’t tell me

71
00:12:04,530 --> 00:12:08,660
Honey, I’m late for work, I’m leaving -Honey

72
00:12:08,930 --> 00:12:12,040
Remember to drink that milk

73
00:12:13,940 --> 00:12:17,840
Yuan Lang, honey

74
00:12:59,970 --> 00:13:08,330
[Whacha doin’]

75
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:24,940
[Off work yet]

76
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:42,240
[Let’s go to the movies this weekend]

77
00:14:02,630 --> 00:14:07,110
[What about it] [Aren’t you satisfied with a cute girlfriend like me]

78
00:14:17,570 --> 00:14:27,750
[K] [Cute] [Round and cute]

79
00:14:42,590 --> 00:14:47,730
Mr.Xiang -Where is Yezi? -She and Zhuxuan went to talk about the program with Mr.Yu

80
00:14:48,100 --> 00:14:51,650
They’ll be back late. Why don’t you call her?

81
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:56,710
OK I will -I’m going to lunch -Please

82
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:21,590
Hello

83
00:15:22,370 --> 00:15:24,250
Hello, and you are?

84
00:15:26,890 --> 00:15:32,250
Hi, I am Yezi’s mother, I’m here to bring her lunch. Where is Yezi, please?

85
00:15:32,700 --> 00:15:38,260
Auntie, Yezi left for a meeting, why don’t you sit here and wait for her? She’ll be back soon

86
00:15:38,610 --> 00:15:40,070
Meeting

87
00:15:42,090 --> 00:15:47,500
She just graduated and she’s already too busy for meals

88
00:15:47,810 --> 00:15:49,520
How can I rest assure?

89
00:15:50,830 --> 00:15:57,110
And she is already 30 years old, and she is not worried about her marriage at all

90
00:15:57,390 --> 00:16:00,950
She is exactly like when she was a kid, I have to worry about her all the time

91
00:16:01,410 --> 00:16:05,230
Auntie, calm down, have some water -Thanks

92
00:16:06,950 --> 00:16:12,760
Son, are you her colleague or?

93
00:16:14,130 --> 00:16:16,060
I am Yezi’s

94
00:16:17,170 --> 00:16:18,570
Friend

95
00:16:19,450 --> 00:16:26,950
You are her friend, has she talked about that to you?

96
00:16:28,380 --> 00:16:34,830
I don’t think so -You don’t know either

97
00:16:36,140 --> 00:16:41,960
My Yezi is indocile and secretive since she was a kid

98
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:47,050
In elementary school once she had a bad grade and teacher asked her to bring home her paper

99
00:16:47,050 --> 00:16:56,480
To ask us to sign, and she hided it away from us until her teacher called home

100
00:16:56,480 --> 00:17:00,840
Saying that where the paper at after three days

101
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:06,600
Her dad and I tried every way to ask her where the paper was and she wouldn’t tell

102
00:17:06,600 --> 00:17:10,700
Do you know where did she hide it? -Where

103
00:17:11,420 --> 00:17:15,260
I found it under the bed when I cleaned the house

104
00:17:15,590 --> 00:17:24,570
What’s more, when she got love letter in high school -That early?

105
00:17:24,830 --> 00:17:32,530
That’s what I said. And the teacher took the letters away and ask us to come to school

106
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:40,540
We asked her who gave her the love letter, you know, she wouldn’t tell again and she even felt wronged

107
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:44,820
How could she not know who gave her the letters? Wasn’t she lying to us?

108
00:17:47,970 --> 00:17:55,380
But my Yezi had a boyfriend in college, that I know

109
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:06,160
Has she talked about that boyfriend to you?

110
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:12,430
No, but we could feel that they were happy together -How?

111
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:20,360
In vacation she’d always lock herself in her room and text to someone until midnight

112
00:18:20,910 --> 00:18:25,220
So we knew they got along well -Right

113
00:18:27,600 --> 00:18:29,110
Do you know that boy?

114
00:18:31,570 --> 00:18:33,480
He is a friend of mine

115
00:18:36,070 --> 00:18:44,250
OK. Do you know why they broke up? Have your friend told you?

116
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:49,970
He might have his own reasons -Yeah, right

117
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:54,410
Did he think less of my girl? -No way

118
00:18:58,380 --> 00:19:00,300
I know what kind of a person he is

119
00:19:03,730 --> 00:19:08,540
I still think that Lin Sen is the best one for her

120
00:19:09,010 --> 00:19:14,320
They grew up together and he is reliable

121
00:19:15,220 --> 00:19:22,540
I also grow up with my friend, he is handsome and educated, and talented

122
00:19:22,840 --> 00:19:29,450
Young man, you might not know Lin Sen, but I know him since he was this little

123
00:19:29,670 --> 00:19:33,120
Yes, mine too, I know him well too

124
00:19:33,420 --> 00:19:37,850
He is tall and handsome and most importantly he is very reliable

125
00:19:38,150 --> 00:19:44,940
There is no use for us to talk about that. Yezi is the one to decide

126
00:19:46,010 --> 00:19:48,130
You are right

127
00:19:51,930 --> 00:19:55,440
Young man, I still don’t know your name

128
00:19:59,070 --> 00:20:04,320
Xiang -What a rare name

129
00:20:10,410 --> 00:20:14,360
Junior got sentenced for injuring other, crying saying goodbye to his parents

130
00:20:15,350 --> 00:20:21,800
16 years old, such a good age, and Dong went to jail for intentional assault

131
00:20:22,500 --> 00:20:25,010
The law will punish him

132
00:20:26,020 --> 00:20:34,550
What’s surprising is that they fought only over a cigarette

133
00:20:41,010 --> 00:20:46,150
Every one makes mistakes. He is still so young, only 16 years old

134
00:20:46,430 --> 00:20:50,340
As the old saying goes, be not ashamed of?mistakes?and thus?make?them crimes

135
00:20:50,600 --> 00:20:53,730
His life just starts

136
00:20:54,630 --> 00:20:58,550
If he really knows about his mistakes and tries to make it right

137
00:20:58,810 --> 00:21:05,150
When he gets out, all of us should give him another chance to start over

138
00:21:21,590 --> 00:21:29,020
Where were we? Anyway young man, I feel nice talking to you

139
00:21:29,280 --> 00:21:36,560
Not every young man can talk to old people like us for that long

140
00:21:37,030 --> 00:21:41,680
But I still don’t know your name

141
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:50,740
Auntie, I feel nice talking to you, too

142
00:21:51,750 --> 00:21:58,550
I’m Xiang -Xiang, what a rare name

143
00:21:59,860 --> 00:22:03,050
Thank you for chatting with me, Xiang

144
00:22:06,340 --> 00:22:07,270
I

145
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,690
I

146
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:30,820
I am not strong as before

147
00:22:50,380 --> 00:22:53,470
Hi Yezi, I forgot to tell you

148
00:22:53,800 --> 00:22:58,770
Liu Xinran said that she’ll going to America with Zhang Daniao for electronic sports game

149
00:22:59,500 --> 00:23:05,670
And also get married over the journey. So she asked us when we could make time to gather

150
00:23:05,930 --> 00:23:12,010
OK -Are you having meetings with Xiang Zeyi lately?

151
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:19,340
Any updates? -Bye, gossip girl

152
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:32,990
No

153
00:23:42,140 --> 00:23:47,080
Dad, mom, we should be here taking you home

154
00:23:47,080 --> 00:23:52,090
You’ve been gone for long -Let me take this, uncle -Thank you

155
00:23:52,090 --> 00:23:56,860
And you are? -Auntie, I am Wu Kai -Wu Kai -Yes

156
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:05,170
I should’ve known -It’s heavy. Let me -It’s fine, we are almost to the car

157
00:24:08,850 --> 00:24:15,270
Is he the intern in your company? He seems nice

158
00:24:15,270 --> 00:24:20,380
Not every young man is willing to work hard

159
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:29,940
We are used to rich kids abroad, they are nothing compared to Wu Kai

160
00:24:32,070 --> 00:24:33,390
Wu Kai

161
00:24:37,110 --> 00:24:38,540
Dad, mom

162
00:24:39,770 --> 00:24:45,440
Wu Kai is my boyfriend -Boy, boyfriend

163
00:24:46,100 --> 00:24:48,510
We’ve been seeing each other for a while

164
00:24:48,770 --> 00:24:50,830
That’s why I brought him with me today

165
00:24:52,110 --> 00:24:57,670
Uncle and auntie, Cheng Xi and I have known each other for long, and

166
00:24:57,950 --> 00:25:04,980
We are tired. We can talk later -Right. Later

167
00:25:06,020 --> 00:25:09,430
Sure, get on the car please

168
00:25:32,270 --> 00:25:33,510
Careful mom

169
00:25:34,830 --> 00:25:36,430
Here, sit please

170
00:25:39,220 --> 00:25:41,980
Why don’t you wait for me downstairs? -Sure

171
00:25:42,970 --> 00:25:48,310
Uncle and auntie, take good rest and I’ll be downstairs

172
00:25:51,270 --> 00:25:57,950
Xi, why don’t you have dinner at home tonight? With us?

173
00:25:59,620 --> 00:26:04,090
I bought you something in the fridge. I had plan for tonight

174
00:26:04,090 --> 00:26:08,490
If you have no other things, Wu is waiting for me

175
00:26:09,770 --> 00:26:18,180
Xi, listen to me. Your boyfriend needs to be someone reliable and grown up

176
00:26:18,470 --> 00:26:28,740
That Mr.Wu is not for you -Mom -Your mom is right

177
00:26:29,020 --> 00:26:32,350
We didn’t take good care of you because of the business

178
00:26:32,660 --> 00:26:38,820
We hope that you can have a real man to take care of you, but not someone younger than you

179
00:26:38,820 --> 00:26:41,800
Who needs you to take care of him -Right

180
00:26:42,620 --> 00:26:45,880
Dad, mom, don’t worry about me

181
00:26:46,440 --> 00:26:52,790
Just take a good rest -Every parent worries

182
00:26:54,280 --> 00:27:00,850
Xi, go to do your things if you are busy. Don’t worry about us

183
00:27:02,560 --> 00:27:06,080
See you later

184
00:27:12,770 --> 00:27:14,930
How about that? Not bad right?

185
00:27:15,790 --> 00:27:21,710
I told you, even playing games, I Zhang Daniao will make it

186
00:27:24,820 --> 00:27:29,510
Mr.Zhang Xiaopeng, you are a different man after you married

187
00:27:29,770 --> 00:27:37,550
You even get luckier -What are you saying? I made it because of my strength

188
00:27:39,120 --> 00:27:43,160
You can say this after you get that international award

189
00:27:44,280 --> 00:27:49,820
I can’t talk better than you but I act sooner than you -What act?

190
00:27:50,850 --> 00:27:53,590
I have a wife now, how about you?

191
00:27:56,150 --> 00:27:58,400
I’m saying this because you are my brother

192
00:27:58,880 --> 00:28:09,630
Lin Sen never gives up on Yezi, make your move soon or you’ll regret it -Fine

193
00:28:09,630 --> 00:28:16,650
Tonight my wife and Yezi and others are having a girls night

194
00:28:17,350 --> 00:28:25,280
Go pick Yezi up, and let the moonlight and the wine do their trick on you

195
00:28:26,350 --> 00:28:27,630
You hear me?

196
00:28:29,690 --> 00:28:32,410
That’s the plan. Be there

197
00:28:47,980 --> 00:28:49,260
Cheers

198
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:56,140
Xinran, when are you leaving? -The day after tomorrow

199
00:28:56,660 --> 00:29:03,830
What’s your first station? -Sun and beach in Hawaii -What about Daniao?

200
00:29:03,830 --> 00:29:09,720
It’s soon. We plan to leave early for the trip and the game is our last station

201
00:29:09,970 --> 00:29:14,790
Daniao said that he wants to take the wedding aura to the game and we might win

202
00:29:15,760 --> 00:29:21,870
The way I see it, Zhang Daniao might be worried that he’d lose the moods to travel with you after you lose

203
00:29:21,870 --> 00:29:24,250
Go away -Sorry I’m late

204
00:29:25,280 --> 00:29:27,390
One coke, please

205
00:29:27,820 --> 00:29:33,930
Xi, are you alright? -Nothing, it’s just, thank you

206
00:29:34,890 --> 00:29:42,540
My parents are back. They are making me kind of uncomfortable -How come?

207
00:29:43,860 --> 00:29:52,390
Here is the thing. My parents went to Argentina when I was ten and they barely came back

208
00:29:52,630 --> 00:29:58,780
Recently they are not as strong and the policies have been changing

209
00:29:59,070 --> 00:30:03,870
So they are driven to come back, so they come back this year

210
00:30:04,260 --> 00:30:09,520
That still counts as a family reunion, why aren’t you cheered up?

211
00:30:09,600 --> 00:30:16,580
Right, why do you look distracted and upset? -I thought I’d feel happy, too

212
00:30:16,860 --> 00:30:24,560
But I can’t describe my feelings -What kind? -Well

213
00:30:25,220 --> 00:30:31,320
You know how I am used to eat without waiting for others, going out without telling anyone

214
00:30:31,590 --> 00:30:35,150
Feeling free to do anything. After they came back

215
00:30:35,460 --> 00:30:42,850
They do take care of every detail of my life, but two more people in life still makes it

216
00:30:43,200 --> 00:30:49,670
Awkward -You mean their coming back messes up your tempos

217
00:30:49,940 --> 00:30:57,950
Yes, like I’m being pushed to change all of my old habits and I can’t even resist

218
00:30:58,690 --> 00:31:06,400
Xi, have you thought that maybe your parents are also adjusting themselves to fit into your life?

219
00:31:10,390 --> 00:31:20,200
I understand you. You know how my parents loved to talk and talk

220
00:31:20,600 --> 00:31:25,720
Sometimes I couldn’t even bear with them

221
00:31:26,410 --> 00:31:34,120
But then I began to realize that that’s their way of expressing love

222
00:31:34,470 --> 00:31:37,810
I might have been used to it before I knew it

223
00:31:38,050 --> 00:31:47,310
If it’s gone one day, I might not bear it -Xi, try to really live with your parents

224
00:31:47,590 --> 00:31:54,220
But not simply sharing a house with them. They love you the most. You’ll know

225
00:31:55,250 --> 00:31:58,770
Thank you for the nice speech

226
00:31:59,050 --> 00:32:02,160
Here I’ll drink to you

227
00:32:03,010 --> 00:32:08,890
To Xi, I hope you can change your on-my-own lifestyle soon and get along well with your parents

228
00:32:09,150 --> 00:32:11,040
Cheers

229
00:32:14,700 --> 00:32:21,600
We also need to celebrate Xinran’s ending of single life and her happily ever after with Daniao

230
00:32:21,870 --> 00:32:26,970
Thank you -Take time to have a baby bird (means niao in Chinese)

231
00:32:27,250 --> 00:32:33,870
Bad girl -I’m not the bad one. There is no better thing than giving birth to next generation

232
00:32:34,140 --> 00:32:38,710
Here, cheers -I take Zhuxuan’s side this time -Fine, thank you

233
00:32:38,990 --> 00:32:42,140
To a little bird

234
00:32:44,260 --> 00:32:48,590
Daniao is waiting on the other block, who is coming with me?

235
00:32:48,870 --> 00:32:52,350
Take me, my husband is working overtime -I’ll take a cab

236
00:32:52,570 --> 00:32:56,760
What about you, Yezi? -I’d like to take a walk

237
00:32:57,020 --> 00:33:00,200
OK, take care

238
00:33:14,610 --> 00:33:15,930
What are you doing here?

239
00:33:17,510 --> 00:33:21,840
Daniao said you just ended dinner. It’s late so I’d like to take you home

240
00:33:22,120 --> 00:33:24,970
No thanks, my home is nearby -That’s why I didn’t drive

241
00:33:25,970 --> 00:33:27,520
Shall we take a walk together?

242
00:33:56,500 --> 00:34:01,380
Every time after drinking with the girls, I’m used to take this road

243
00:34:02,080 --> 00:34:09,320
It’s quiet and comfortable, a nice way to sort out the thoughts

244
00:34:11,250 --> 00:34:17,250
But having someone walking together also feels nice

245
00:34:27,890 --> 00:34:29,460
Are you familiar with the roads?

246
00:34:40,040 --> 00:34:45,250
I’ve also walked on this road for many times

247
00:34:49,970 --> 00:34:59,700
Not on my own, but with a tempered woman

248
00:35:04,170 --> 00:35:06,910
You are the one always on my back

249
00:35:24,660 --> 00:35:31,280
I’ve seen her drunk and crashed on the garbage can

250
00:35:37,430 --> 00:35:48,280
But she managed to stand up on her own and walked away

251
00:35:57,620 --> 00:36:01,620
I’ve seen her jumping over joy

252
00:36:10,560 --> 00:36:20,270
I’ve seen her standing in front of the garbage can and thinking

253
00:36:22,500 --> 00:36:30,900
She stood there for long but I still didn’t have the courage to come out and say

254
00:36:34,840 --> 00:36:36,080
Long time no see

255
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:39,680
Or

256
00:36:42,240 --> 00:36:44,050
See you next time

257
00:37:22,860 --> 00:37:26,470
I knew why she stared at that simple painting

258
00:37:30,270 --> 00:37:33,480
Why she was always alone

259
00:37:36,390 --> 00:37:39,310
Why she always chose to pretend to be strong

260
00:37:41,860 --> 00:37:44,220
But I didn’t have the courage to say that

261
00:37:46,770 --> 00:37:48,030
I’m here

262
00:37:50,910 --> 00:37:52,440
Long time no see

263
00:37:55,480 --> 00:37:57,320
I walked you home

264
00:37:59,540 --> 00:38:01,070
And

265
00:38:04,390 --> 00:38:06,180
Good night

266
00:38:30,140 --> 00:38:31,590
I’ve been thinking

267
00:38:35,070 --> 00:38:38,380
If god’d give me another chance

268
00:38:38,690 --> 00:38:41,680
To say hi to you again

269
00:38:45,020 --> 00:38:46,560
How are you?

270
00:38:49,630 --> 00:38:51,730
To say good night to you

271
00:39:01,110 --> 00:39:13,320
But now I know, what we’ve missed can’t be made up by greetings and good nights

272
00:39:17,180 --> 00:39:19,190
I want to give you that late promise

273
00:39:22,980 --> 00:39:24,900
I want to make you happy

274
00:39:30,650 --> 00:39:32,080
Yezi

275
00:39:36,080 --> 00:39:38,000
I’m trying to make it happen

276
00:39:43,830 --> 00:39:45,800
Please have faith in me

277
00:39:47,110 --> 00:39:48,900
Will you?
